name: @BoredApe9460 on Tour // Unsplash.com
description: Photo by Dan Meyers @dmey503 // I was going through some old photos and came across this picture I took in 2014 in the West Bank (Palestine). This was done by Banksy, which I didn't learn until a couple years later. I paid a Palestinian cab driver to take me to their side of the wall and took a few photos of the "graffiti"/art with my iPhone. The West Bank is walled off like a prison and heavily guarded by the Israelis. For those reasons, of all the "graffiti" I saw, this one resonated the most with me. I hope this pic introduces others to this amazing piece of art or gives some context to those who have seen it before. // 1 of 1 Remix created by @FutureNow_Art, part owners of #BAYC 9460
